WEBVTT

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.656
And this street anatomy is so captivating

00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:04.400
because it is the furthest removed
from the medical world.

00:10:04.920 --> 00:10:06.536
It forces you to look at it,

00:10:06.560 --> 00:10:08.800
and confront your own
perceptions about anatomy,

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:11.656
whether you find it beautiful,

00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:12.896
gross,

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:14.136
morbid

00:10:14.160 --> 00:10:16.160
or awe-inspiring, like I do.

00:10:16.920 --> 00:10:18.856
That it elicits these responses at all

00:10:18.880 --> 00:10:22.440
is due to our intimate
and often changing relationship with it.

00:10:24.120 --> 00:10:26.336
All of the artists
that I showed you here today

00:10:26.360 --> 00:10:29.016
referenced medical
illustrations for their art.

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:30.256
But for them,